[Student "S"]
{When partner opens 1\S you have a pretty normal Jacoby 2NT response. He next says 3\S.  

Your partner has a better than minimum hand with 6 \Ss. However, you have an average hand with no controls to show so you use the Principle of Fast Arrival and bid 4\S. Everyone passes.}

